    {
      "id": "72",
      "name": "Properties",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "customize",
          "data": {
            "data": {
              "parsed_content": [
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "Relationships",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 3,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 4910,
                      "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/01/03/237301566/59da6a8cbcffa112e5d2b63788d7051e_1480677671668697202.png",
                      "menu_id": 10,
                      "name": "Руккхадевата",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    },
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 7471,
                      "icon_url": "",
                      "name": "Buer",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Greater Lord Rukkhadevata and Lesser Lord Kusanali are the avatars of Irminsul, whose consciousness is linked to it. Rukkhadevata saved Irminsul from forbidden knowledge several thousand years ago, but later it was infected again during the",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "text",
                      "ep_id": 7089,
                      "icon_url": "",
                      "name": "Khaenri'ahn cataclysm",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": ". The forbidden knowledge spread to Rukkhadevata's own consciousness, so 500 years later Nahida erased the Greater Lord from Irminsul to stop the corruption. Since then, no one who belongs to Teyvat remembers the Greater Lord.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 5748,
                      "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/11/237301566/9637c661f54d176aea6cc2ef4dca351c_8088405348288109265.png",
                      "menu_id": 23,
                      "name": "Ведьмин шабаш",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Witches from the Hexenzirkel study Irminsul. On some of them (for example,",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "text",
                      "ep_id": 6367,
                      "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/07/25/237301566/279e2e1b961d770f2b89f649906b32f7_5277376151613556261.png",
                      "menu_id": 10,
                      "name": "Alice",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": ") Irminsul has no influence.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 4583,
                      "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/11/08/237301566/3ca9b9e2138195540f079c470acfbce5_2710094818565120265.png",
                      "menu_id": 10,
                      "name": "Скарамучча",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Scaramouche erased himself from Irminsul to try to change the past, but it only rewrote people's memories of the past, as Irminsul can't change reality.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 7085,
                      "icon_url": "",
                      "name": "Сошедшие",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    },
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 13,
                      "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/11/19/70239714/1fb2086af3c7933af37eda1ff9084317_3480344329760444937.png",
                      "menu_id": 2,
                      "name": "Элой",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Irminsul does not influence beings from other worlds.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Traveler's Sibling",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "The information about the sibling was intentionally changed in Irminsul.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 7034,
                      "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/10/04/237301566/2285a2d002f2043abe9bddf65a46f891_2725272071367240618.png",
                      "menu_id": 23,
                      "name": "Академия Сумеру",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "It is a common practice among the scholars of Sumeru to contact Irminsul. When Irminsul was contaminated with forbidden knowledge, many scholars went mad during the Satyavada Life stage. They believed that since Irminsul contained divine knowledge, touching such knowledge without the proper preparations and abilities would only lead to one's mind caving in on itself.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 7106,
                      "icon_url": "",
                      "name": "Fatui",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "The Fatui know Irminsul's structure. From the information they received, they learned that the sky of Teyvat was fake.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "Related Entries",
